{"tid":523580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 工作困擾  90後燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-01-08T16:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T08:34:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7c2396292e773d2a07c9279f3935ffa1354a62","tid":523580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"青衣長青邨青榕樓有青年燒炭亡，下午5時許，一名姓余（31歲）女子下班返家時，發現屋內傳出燒焦氣味，查看下揭發由其胞弟(22歲)的房間傳出，於是拍門呼喊，但沒有回應，試圖開門又發現房門反鎖，大驚報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方聯同消防接報趕至，破門入房，發現青年昏迷倒臥在房內，旁邊有一盤燒過的炭，救護員將事主送院，惜搶救後不治。現場並無檢獲遺書，警方經初步調查後，相信事件無可疑，案件列作自殺。據了解，青年生前受<span style=\"color: red;\">工作問題困擾</span>，不排除因此輕生。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180108/bkn-20180108192359578-0108_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180108%2Fbkn-20180108192359578-0108_00822_001.html&d=DcuFZlbARcRJwNHQWwNGxdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=54aefb04\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180108/bkn-20180108192359578-0108_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0efebdf5ca84b76f67e5321eb7ddefd8573855bb","tid":523580,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:34:55.000Z","msg":"公屋仔 WFC"},{"pid":"162a85dc1c32f8161014842b59a4159c38249dd5","tid":523580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"青年生前受工作問題困擾<br />\n青年生前受工作問題困擾<br />\n青年生前受工作問題困擾"},{"pid":"bb4a5075736b2280de06a28504ce7ae9970465c8","tid":523580,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162a85dc1c32f8161014842b59a4159c38249dd5","tid":523580,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"青年生前受工作問題困擾<br />\n青年生前受工作問題困擾<br />\n青年生前受工作問題困擾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"冇感情問題，sad"},{"pid":"bba35175f473cb07de547bc82d6eec636a758ead","tid":523580,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T16:42:35